<h1>How to make Waffles</h1>
<h2>By MyLeah Dudley-Ellis</h2>
<p> I like to make waffles on Saturday mornings since I have time to do it, and it is a nice way to start my weekend. I enjoy adding chocolate chips and cinnamon to my waffles to give it a different taste..</p>
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul>
<li>pancake mix(your choice)</li>
<li>two eggs</li>
<li> chocolate chips </li>
<li>vegetable oil</li>
<li>Milk</li>
<li>Butter</li>
<li>Cinnamon</li>
<h4>What to do</h4>
<ol>
<li>crack 2 eggs</li>
<li>Mix pancake mix mix, add milk or water, add chocolate chips,and add cinnamon</li>
<li>heat up waffle maker and add butter or oil</li>
<li>when wafflemaker is hot add batter and flip</li>
<li> take waffle off waffle maker </li>
<li>enjoy!</li>
</ol>
